      <title>惠誉在出售收益不佳后下调丹格特工业的评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/fitch-downgrades-dangote-industries-after-soft-sale-proceeds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级下调了对丹格特工业有限公司信用度的评估，理由包括“该集团的流动性状况因处置收益低于预期而严重恶化”，并将其评级列入负面观察名单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/fitch-downgrades-dangote-industries-after-soft-sale-proceeds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:39:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛称在标普 500 指数下跌 5% 后买入通常可获利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/goldman-says-buying-s-p-500-after-5-drop-is-usually-profitable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团对四十年数据的分析显示，在过去一个月出现如此大规模的暴跌之后买入美国股票通常都是有利可图的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/goldman-says-buying-s-p-500-after-5-drop-is-usually-profitable</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:37:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全文：洲际酒店集团首席执行官谈业绩、回购、亚洲市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/in-full-ihg-ceo-on-performance-buybacks-asian-market-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洲际酒店集团首席执行官 Elie Maalouf 在彭博电视台谈论这家全球酒店巨头的业绩，此前该公司公布了上半年收益超出预期的业绩。Maalouf 还讨论了回购、亚洲市场等问题。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/in-full-ihg-ceo-on-performance-buybacks-asian-market-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:23:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通称套利交易的解体尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/unraveling-of-carry-trade-not-done-yet-jpmorgan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通全球外汇策略联席主管 Arindam Sandilya 表示：“至少在投机投资界，套利交易平仓已经完成 50%-60%。”他在彭博电视上发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/unraveling-of-carry-trade-not-done-yet-jpmorgan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:20:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国债下跌，避险需求减弱，焦点转向拍卖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-treasuries-fall-as-haven-bid-fades-traders-focus-on-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球对避险资产的需求减弱，美国国债价格下跌，市场目前转向 580 亿美元的拍卖，作为对投资者兴趣的下一个考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-treasuries-fall-as-haven-bid-fades-traders-focus-on-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 08:06:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美保留 310 亿美元股息作为沙特王国的主要分红</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/aramco-keeps-31-billion-dividend-in-key-payout-to-saudi-arabia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管利润下降，沙特阿美仍将季度股息维持在 310 亿美元，因为对于沙特阿拉伯政府数万亿美元的经济转型计划而言，股息变得越来越重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/aramco-keeps-31-billion-dividend-in-key-payout-to-saudi-arabia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 05:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市从 2008 年以来最严重跌势中反弹，日本领涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/asian-stocks-rebound-from-worst-rout-since-2008-led-by-japan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国经济硬着陆担忧导致区域基准指数出现 2008 年以来最大单日跌幅后，受逢低买盘推动，亚洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/asian-stocks-rebound-from-worst-rout-since-2008-led-by-japan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:06:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着科技股三天抛售潮的消退，美国股指期货上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-stock-futures-bounce-back-after-three-day-global-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国经济放缓和科技股估值过高，全球股市经历了为期三天的抛售，美国股指期货周一上涨，一些买家纷纷涌入市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-stock-futures-bounce-back-after-three-day-global-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 00:59:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着“常态”回归，美国期货价格小幅走高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市收复了周一的部分失地，美国期货小幅上涨，因为交易员在全球市场抛售的残骸中寻找便宜货。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 23:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球市场暴跌势头减弱，油价持于七个月低点附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球股市动荡有所缓解，且利比亚最大油田停产使人们的注意力重新集中在中东地区，油价维持在七个月低点附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 23:18:29 GMT</pubDate>
